      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/01/181140897/26b9736a2d14fc4162b2448963f45695_8466766641269895929.png",
                "id": "talent12568",
                "key": "云来剑法",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "云来剑法"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成3点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>，生成手牌<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">雷楔</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/01/181140897/855f8d96be42fe05d7f7d66b60fad1a6_4765143091355118583.png",
                "id": "talent36129",
                "key": "星斗归位",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "星斗归位"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成4点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>，对所有敌方后台角色造成3点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/01/181140897/9950bc530ec62d8e01daf47fe1229216_4856607041885736305.png",
                "id": "talent19786",
                "key": "天街巡游",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "天街巡游"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">事件牌</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">战斗行动</span>：将刻晴切换到场上，立刻使用星斗归位。本次星斗归位会为刻晴附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">雷元素附魔</span>，但是不会再生成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">雷楔</span>。</p><p>（刻晴使用星斗归位时，如果此牌在手中：不会再生成雷楔，而是改为<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">舍弃</span>此牌，并为刻晴附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">雷元素附魔</span>）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/16/47826599/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_1037120477062477561.png",
                "id": "talent10773",
                "key": "雷楔",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/16/47826599/d6793b3314d1b255f49f2ba1ec500b38_4643215404210026134.png",
                "title": "雷楔"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着雷元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超载</span>：本伤害+2，目标强制切换到下一个角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超导</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">感电</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">原激化</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下2次草元素或雷元素伤害+1的[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">激化领域</span>]</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/16/47826599/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_5185338529573742417.png",
                "id": "talent29491",
                "key": "雷元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "雷元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">穿透伤害</span></strong></p><p>穿透伤害无法受到伤害加成，但是也无法被护盾、伤害免疫等效果抵消。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">战斗行动</span></strong></p><p>我方执行了一次战斗行动后，会轮到对方行动。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">打出具有此规则的手牌是一个战斗行动，而非快速行动。</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">舍弃</span></strong></p><p>通过行动牌或角色技能的效果，将行动牌从手牌或牌库中弃置。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">雷元素附魔</span></strong></p><p>所附属角色造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>变为<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>：2</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/16/47826599/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_694520085672363781.png",
                "id": "talent743",
                "key": "规则术语",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "规则术语"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
